channel.description: Ok you prolly know me since i have a lot of problems last problem. Ok so i got the moparscape client and im using phonescape as source. So i made an acc and change my skills al to lvl 99 (lol). And after lets say half an hour my acc doesnt work anymore and it says your acc is already logged in try again or make a new one. I made a new 1 and then the same thing happened half an hour later. PLZ reply.
